item.description:
@doomsday wrote:

im just learning aryan,

i need to know hwo to make it click on the entrance to the tokkul cave(fight caves) and click on strenght(instead of attack) and then wait until it gets out

here is what i have so far

public class TokkulGetter extends Script {
	
	public static String[] commands = { "tokkul" };

    private int OBJ_ENTRANCE = 9356;//cave entrance id


    public boolean start(String cmd, String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Tokkul Getter Started!");
        return true;
    }
    public long run(long lastExecution) {
   	int cave = findObject(OBJ_ENTRANCE);
        if(cave != -1) {
	atObject(cave, 1);
	log("Clicking on the cave entrance");
	return random(10000,40000);
	} else{
	log("We are currently in the cave. Waiting...");
	return random(10000,40000);
    }

 }

}
